strings: <voice_0x01001CBF><se_high>Princess Medea: I really treasure these moments we get to spend together, <hero>.

<voice_0x01001CC0><se_high>Princess Medea: I know how dangerous it will be to fight Rhapthorne. I know you're risking your life
for us.
<voice_0x01001CC1><se_high>Princess Medea: This could be the last chance we get to speak before the battle, <hero>.
<voice_0x01001CC3><se_high>Princess Medea: The whole world is depending on you.
<voice_0x01001CC4><se_high>Princess Medea: But I'm happy that our fate is in your hands...
